messages.messageBody:
The Family RUNning site is down and Holly and I need to leave for an
out of town wedding soon.

Someone was unable to view that video, and I wrote to Lee to see if it
was anywhere else, and I have this note I was going to post.

If someone else is willing pass this on to the person who asked
directly to to add it to that discussion at RUN or both, I'd really
appreciate it.

Lee wrote:

I was probably to post it on YouTube in a few days....I'm doing a
bunch of health care videos there right now.
But I don't understand why she can't see it there/ I wonder if she
needs to restart her browser.

The question was here:
http://familyrun.ning.com/profiles/blogs/new-little-video-of-me-about

Thanks!
